 Varoma dish into position and weigh in red bell pepper and macadamia nuts. Add red onion and corn kernels to Varoma dish, re-insert Varoma tray with chicken, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>3-5 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>, or until chicken is fully cooked."},{"content":"Remove Varoma and transfer chicken onto a serving platter. Transfer steamed vegetables into a serving bowl and add cilantro leaves and remaining jalapeño sauce."},{"content":"Remove simmering basket with spatula and allow freekeh to drain. Transfer drained freekeh into serving bowl with the vegetables and season to taste with onion salt and pepper."},{"content":"Fill a lettuce leaf with the freekeh salad, top with a spiced chicken tenderloin, a spoonful of reserved guacamole, extra jalapeño chilies and sour cream to serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable Stock Paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","4 portions"]}